<h2><strong>Why Use a Wedding Guest List App Instead of a Spreadsheet?</strong></h2>
<p>Manual spreadsheets and scattered notes lead to version control nightmares. One partner updates row 47; the other emails an old copy to the venue. The result? Vendor miscounts affect roughly 30% of weddings that rely on fragmented documents.</p>
<p>A centralized app solves this with:</p>
